# MTG skill workspace — built decks, collection exports, and the card database all live
# under .mtg/ (or wherever $MTG_HOME points). Generated/personal data, not source, so
# ignore the whole folder. The skills create it on demand; sync decks + collection with the
# mtg-sync skill instead of committing them here (see SYNCING.md).
.mtg/

# Python bytecode from the bundled helper scripts.
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Test/coverage artifacts (CI generates these; not source).
.coverage
htmlcov/
comment.md
test_output.txt

# Claude Code local config and worktrees — not part of the published skills.
.claude/

# Local design docs (ADRs etc.) — kept locally, not committed.
docs/
